  ('promotion-7c9828ae-moex-00090', 'promotion-7c9828ae', 'promotion-7c9828ae-moex-110-cc9133e4', 'sub-promotion-7c9828ae-03', NULL, 'essay', '國內一直有人提倡我國應以北歐福利國家為標竿，大幅提升各項福利措
